Stephen McNally https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stephen_McNally 0 Stephen McNally (July 29, 1911 – June 4, 1994) was an American actor remembered mostly for his appearances in many Westerns and action films. He often played hard-hearted characters or villains. Stephen_McNally ( July_29_,_1911 – June_4_,_1994 ) was an_American_actor remembered mostly for his_appearances in many_Westerns_and_action_films .
